title: The Peter Schiff Show - 2011 Mar 23 WE [sebaygo1]
description:
.
							
The Peter Schiff Show
Wednesday, 23 March 2011


[sebaygo1]


Wednesday's guests are:

Walter Molony, spokesman for the National Association of Realtors, on why tight credit's to blame for February's miserable housing numbers.

Robert Murphy, adjunct scholar at the Mises Institute & author of "The Politically Incorrect Guide to Capitalism," on why trade deficits are no big deal. 



Michael Pento guest hosts again today. Peter should return live tomorrow.
